darks.codec
类 ObjectCoder

java.lang.Object
  darks.codec.ObjectCoder

public class ObjectCoder
extends java.lang.Object

ObjectCoder is the main API class for developer. It uses DefaultCodec as default codec. Developer can customize own codec for the coder. Developer can use CodecConfig to configure codec parameters.
Example: 

  ObjectCoder coder = new ObjectCoder();
  coder.getCodecConfig().setEndianType(EndianType.LITTLE);
  coder.getCodecConfig().setTotalLengthType(TotalLengthType.HEAD_BODY);
  coder.getCodecConfig().setAutoLength(false);
  coder.getCodecConfig().setCacheType(CacheType.LOCAL);
  coder.getCodecConfig().addWrap(new IdentifyWrapper(new OCInt16(0xfafb)));
  coder.getCodecConfig().addWrap(VerifyWrapper.CRC16());
      ...
  SendMessage sm = ...
  byte[] bytes = oc.encode(sm);
      ...
  RecvMessage rm = ...
  oc.decode(bytes, rm);
      ...

方法详细信息

decode

public OCObject decode(byte[] bytes,
                       java.lang.Object source)
                throws java.io.IOException
Decode message java object. Java object will construct the OCObject to decode data really.

参数：
bytes - Message bytes array.
source - Decode target java object.
返回：
If successful decoding, return OCObject. Otherwise return null. If runtime exception occurred when encoding, it will throw DecodingException, ReflectException and other wrapper's OCException.
抛出：
java.io.IOException
